LAN (Local Area Network) connects local devices together  
WAN (Wide Area Network) connects LANs together and operates over the Internet

What type of network a computer in local is connected to?  
- ✅ LAN  
- WAN  
- Internet

What type of network could connect the Holberton HQ office with the Holberton-Gandi space?  
- ✅ WAN  
- LAN  
- Internet

What network do you use when you browse www.google.com from your smartphone (not connected to Wi-Fi)?  
- ✅ Internet  
- LAN  
- WAN
